items.title: 81 monkeys, meth found in car linked to wildlife smuggling network
items.description: A patrol stopped the vehicle and troops found 81 macaques stuffed into blue net bags.

items.title: Jets cornerback Kris Boyd critically injured in NYC shooting, reports say
items.description: Boyd was reportedly found shot in the abdomen in Midtown Manhattan and was rushed to the hospital.

items.title: Declassified Amelia Earhart records include her last known communications
items.description: The documents include military reports about the search as well as memos, telegrams and newspaper clippings.

items.title: FAA lifts emergency order that slashed flights at 40 major U.S. airports
items.description: The Federal Aviation Administration says it is lifting all restrictions on commercial flights that were imposed during the government shutdown.

items.title: Ousted Bangladeshi Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina sentenced to death
items.description: Former Bangladeshi Prime Minister Sheikh Hasina has been sentenced to death over a deadly crackdown on anti-government protests last year.
